<h4>Proton pump inhibitors (PPIs)</h4>
<ul>
	<li>PPIs cause your stomach to make less acid, which helps prevent heartburn.</li>
	<li>Many PPIs are prescription only, but some are available over the counter.</li>
	<li>They are taken as pills.</li>
</ul>
